nalExpansions" id="External Expansions"><span class="hitbox_span"><span class="underline_span">External Expansions</span></span></a></dd><dd class="nav_item"><a href="/openmusictheory_reskinned/internalExpansions" id="Internal Expansions"><span class="hitbox_span"><span class="underline_span">Internal Expansions</span></span></a></dd></dl></li><li class="nav_section"><dl><dt class="nav_header">Sonata Form </dt> <dd class="nav_item"><a href="/openmusictheory_reskinned/SonataTheory-intro" id="Introduction to Sonata Theory"><span class="hitbox_span"><span class="underline_span">Introduction to Sonata Theory</span></span></a></dd><dd class="nav_item"><a href="/openmusictheory_reskinned/SonataTheory-exposition" id="Sonata form: exposition types"><span class="hitbox_span"><span class="underline_span">Sonata form: exposition types</span></span></a></dd><dd class="nav_item"><a href="/openmusictheory_reskinned/sonataStructuralPointsOfArrival" id="Structural Points of Arrival"><span class="hitbox_span"><span class="underline_span">Structural Points of Arrival</span></span></a></dd><dd class="nav_item"><a href="/openmusictheory_reskinned/sonataThematicModules" id="Thematic Modules"><span class="hitbox_span"><span class="underline_span">Thematic Modules</span></span></a></dd><dd class="nav_item"><a href="/openmusictheory_reskinned/sonataRecap" id="Sonata form: the recapitulation"><span class="hitbox_span"><span class="underline_span">Sonata form: the recapitulation</span></span></a></dd><dd class="nav_item"><a href="/openmusictheory_reskinned/sonataDevelopment" id="Sonata form: the development"><span class="hitbox_span"><span class="underline_span">Sonata form: the development</span></span></a></dd><dd class="nav_item"><a href="/openmusictheory_reskinned/sonataFramingModules" id="Sonata form: framing modules (intro &amp; coda)"><span class="hitbox_span"><span class="underline_span">Sonata form: framing modules (intro &amp; coda)</span></span></a></dd></dl></li><li class="nav_se