ith galant schemata"><span class="hitbox_span"><span class="underline_span">Improvising a sentence with galant schemata</span></span></a></dd></dl></li><li class="nav_section"><dl><dt class="nav_header">(Post-tonal) Basics</dt> <dd class="nav_item"><a href="/openmusictheory_reskinned/pitch-class" id="Pitch (class)"><span class="hitbox_span"><span class="underline_span">Pitch (class)</span></span></a></dd><dd class="nav_item"><a href="/openmusictheory_reskinned/interval-class" id="Interval (class)."><span class="hitbox_span"><span class="underline_span">Interval (class).</span></span></a></dd><dd class="nav_item"><a href="/openmusictheory_reskinned/mod12" id="Modular 12 arithmetic"><span class="hitbox_span"><span class="underline_span">Modular 12 arithmetic</span></span></a></dd></dl></li><li class="nav_section"><dl><dt class="nav_header">(Post-tonal) Organizing Forces</dt> <dd class="nav_item"><a href="/openmusictheory_reskinned/scales2" id="Collections and Scales"><span class="hitbox_span"><span class="underline_span">Collections and Scales</span></span></a></dd><dd class="nav_item"><a href="/openmusictheory_reskinned/symmetryAndCentricity" id="Symmetry and Centricity"><span class="hitbox_span"><span class="underline_span">Symmetry and Centricity</span></span></a></dd></dl></li><li class="nav_section"><dl><dt class="nav_header">(Post-tonal) Set Theory</dt> <dd class="nav_item"><a href="/openmusictheory_reskinned/normalOrder" id="Normal Order"><span class="hitbox_span"><span class="underline_span">Normal Order</span></span></a></dd><dd class="nav_item"><a href="/openmusictheory_reskinned/transposition" id="Tranposition"><span class="hitbox_span"><span class="underline_span">Tranposition</span></span></a></dd><dd class="nav_item"><a href="/openmusictheory_reskinned/inversion" id="Inversion"><span class="hitbox_span"><span class="underline_span">Inversion</span></span></a></dd><dd class="nav_item"><a href="/openmusictheory_reskinned/setClassAndPrimeForm1" id="Set Clas